{
  "stem": "19218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then they put us on trucks, and they took us to that ghetto Pruzana, P-I-U-Z-A-N-Y.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And of course, the Jewish community in that ghetto, they just put us in a home, and every room contained a family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- we were five of us-- excuse me, it was four of us-- my mother and father, myself, and my sister-- four of us, we were in that one room, because there were probably five, six other families in the same house.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all had a room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there wasn't much space in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that camp, of course, we were getting certain rations, not enough to die, but not enough to live either.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I was taken to a camp to build a highway in the forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was taken away from the family, even though we were in that camp, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was taken away, and I worked in there-- it was most of the summer that I worked in that camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and it could have been 1942.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really do not recall [BACKGROUND NOISE] the exact dates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember my father visited me once, because they have-- the Germans have killed one guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have actually taken three guys out just to execute them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no reason for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they-- two of them escaped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One was killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this two made their way back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, when they came, they said, probably by now everybody is shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when my father came-- he was delivering food to our camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when he came there, I had a lot of clothes, dirty clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I send it back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, when he brought the clothes, my whole family, he's dead, he's dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
